---
import Article from "../../components/article-with-image/Article.astro";
import Nature from "../../svg/Nature.astro";
---

<Article title="Contacto" alignText="right">
  <figure slot="after">
    <Nature />
    <figcaption>Paisaje</figcaption>
  </figure>
  <p>
    Si deseas contactarme o tienes alguna consulta, no dudes en enviarme un
    mensaje. Estoy aqu√≠ para ayudarte y escuchar tus ideas.
  </p>
  <form id="ContactForm">
    <input
      type="text"
      name="name"
      placeholder="Nombre"
      autocomplete="name"
      required
    />
    <input
      type="email"
      name="email"
      placeholder="Correo"
      autocomplete="email"
      required
    />
    <textarea
      name="message"
      cols={30}
      rows={6}
      placeholder="Mensaje"
      autocomplete="off"
      required></textarea>
    <button type="submit"> Enviar</button>
  </form>
</Article>
<style>
  figure {
    display: flex;
    flex: 1;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 20rem;
  }

  figcaption {
    text-align: center;
    display: none;
  }

  p {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  input[type="text"],
  input[type="email"],
  textarea {
    border-color: var(--color-secondary-dark);
    color: var(--color-gray);
    transition: all 0.15s ease-in-out;
  }

  input[type="text"]:focus,
  input[type="email"]:focus,
  textarea:focus {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    outline: none;
  }

  button[type="submit"] {
    background-color: var(--white);
    user-select: none;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  button[type="submit"]:hover {
    filter: brightness(75%);
  }

  #ContactForm {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    margin-top: 0.7rem;
  }

  #ContactForm input,
  #ContactForm textarea {
    background-color: transparent;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--gray-color);
    padding: 0.76rem;
    outline: none;
    border-bottom: 0.08rem solid;
  }

  #ContactForm input {
    width: calc(50% - 0.35rem); /* Width - Gap */
  }

  #ContactForm textarea {
    width: 100%;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  #ContactForm button {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 1.21rem;
    padding: 0.7rem 0 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.18rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  #ContactForm button:hover {
    filter: brightness(0.8);
  }

  .buttonError {
    color: white !important;
    background-color: red !important;
    animation: fill 750ms ease-in forwards;
  }

  .buttonSuccess {
    color: white !important;
    background-color: green !important;
    animation: fill 750ms ease-in forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fill {
    0% {
      clip-path: circle(5% at 50% 50%);
    }
    100% {
      clip-path: circle(100% at 50% 50%);
    }
  }
</style>
